title: 141: Heisman hopefuls, CFB playoffs and Week 13 NFL recap
itunes:title: 141: Heisman hopefuls, CFB playoffs and Week 13 NFL recap
description:
Former NFL scouts Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks discuss which college football stars have the best shot of taking home the Heisman Trophy and also preview the playoffs in the race to the National Championship. DJ and Bucky also break down the Week 13 action around the NFL.
